Summary: Lights coming down from the sky
divs: Sighting DetailsWe were filming the trees swaying in the wind. We didn't even see the lights when we were filming. When we played the video back we saw the lights coming down through the clouds. You can clearly see one of the last ones cut a hole in the sky. We have a HD version of this.
